channel.title: Need a Complier
channel.description:
You must be thinking im a noob aye? Well im not, Im making a server helper for people and i need a small complier, 4 lines Max. Something like,
Title welcome to (name) (script)(script)(script)(script)(script)(script) echo Finished exit
Something like that just with the script filled out with the complier script. So if u could post a reply , Send me a personal message or talk to me on msn and send me the code. Thank you. :)
